      "number": 9,
      "problem": "Two disks with moments of inertia 3 kg·m² and 5 kg·m² are spinning about the same axis with angular velocities 4 rad/s and 2 rad/s, then locked together. Find the final angular velocity.",
      "image": null,
      "step_by_step": [
        {
          "step": "Conservation of angular momentum",
          "explanation": "$I_1 \\omega_1 + I_2 \\omega_2 = (I_1+I_2) \\omega_f$"
        },
        {
          "step": "Solve for $\\omega_f$",
